texttool_globals_toast___dashboard__drive_select_ai_disabled_reason__battery_low = TextObject(bs_BA="Sistem asistencije Audi drive select ne može odabrati režim\nAudi drive select, jer je punjenje baterije suviše nisko.", cs_CZ="Asistent Audi drive select nemůže zvolit režim Audi drive\nselect, protože stav baterie je příliš nízký.", da_DK="Audi drive select assistant kan ikke vælge Audi drive\nselect-indstillingen, da batteriopladningen er for lav.", de_DE="Der Audi drive select assistant kann den Audi drive select\nModus nicht auswählen, da die Batterieladung zu gering ist.", el_GR="Ο Audi drive select assistant δεν μπορ. να επιλέξ.τη λειτουρ-\nγία Audi drive select, διότι τ.φορτ.τ.μπατ.είναι πολύ χαμηλό.", en_GB="The Audi drive select assistant cannot select the Audi drive\nselect mode because the battery charge is too low.", es_ES="El asistente del Audi drive select no puede seleccionar ningún\nmodo porque la carga de la batería es insuficiente.", fi_FI="Audi drive select assistant ei voi valita Audi drive select -tilaa,\nkoska akun lataustaso on liian alhainen.", fr_FR="L'Audi drive select assistant ne peut pas sélectionner le mode\nde l'Audi drive select car la batterie est trop déchargée.", hr_HR="Audi drive select assistant ne može odabrati Audi drive select\nmodus jer se napunjenost baterije premala.", hu_HU="Az Audi drive select assistant nem tudja kiválasztani az Audi\ndrive select módot, mert az akkutöltöttség túl alacsony.", it_IT="L'Audi drive select assistant non può selezionare la modalità\nAudi drive select: la carica della batteria è troppo bassa.", nl_NL="De Audi drive select assistant kan de Audi drive select-modus\nniet selecteren omdat de acculading te laag is.", no_NO="Audi drive select-assistenten kan ikke velge Audi drive\nselect-modusen fordi batterinivået er for lavt.", pl_PL="Audi drive select assistant nie może wybrać trybu Audi drive\nselect, ponieważ akumulator jest zbyt słabo naładowany.", pt_PT="O assistente Audi drive select não pode selecionar o modo\nAudi drive select pois a carga da bateria é muito reduzida.", ro_RO="Audi drive select assistant nu poate selecta modul Audi drive\nselect, deoarece nivelul de încărcare a bateriei este prea mic.", ru_RU="Audi drive select assistant не может выбрать режим Audi\ndrive select из-за слишком низкого заряда аккумулятора.", sk_SK="Audi drive select assistant nemôže zvoliť režim Audi drive\nselect, pretože je príliš nízka úroveň nabitia akumulátora.", sl_SI="Asistenca Audi drive select zaradi prenizke napetosti akum.\nne more izbrati načina sistema Audi drive select.", sr_RS="Audi drive select assistant ne može da izabere Audi drive\nselect režim, jer je punjenje baterije suviše nisko.", sv_SE="Audi drive select-assistenten kan inte välja Audi drive\nselect-läge, eftersom batterinivån är för låg.", tr_TR="Akü şarjı çok düşük olduğu için, Audi drive select assistant\nAudi drive select modunu seçemiyor.", uk_UA="Audi drive select assistant не може вибрати режим Audi\ndrive select, оскільки заряд акумулятора занадто низький.")
